The '''X32 Digital Mixing Console''' is a [[Digital audio|digital]] [[mixing console]] conceived and designed by German manufacturer [[Behringer]].  The console features 40-input [[Audio channel|channel]]s, 25-[[Audio bus|bus]], 32 [[XLR connector|XLR]] [[microphone]] input and 16 XLR output busses.  The console features 25 100mm motorised [[Audio fader|fader]]s, a user assignable control panel, [[Ethernet]] connectivity and an [[iPad]] and [[iPhone]] control application.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.musicradar.com/reviews/tech/behringer-x32-digital-mixing-console-567208 |title=Behringer X32 Digital Mixing Console |publisher=musicradar.com }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.americanmusical.com/Item--i-BEH-X32-LIST |title=Behringer X32 Total-Recall Digital Mixing Console |publisher=americanmusical.com }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fullcompass.com/product/400830.html |title=Behringer X32 – 32-Channel Digital Console |publisher=fullcompass.com }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://bestdjstuff.com |title=bestdjstuff.com |publisher=Marry Stalon }}</ref>

